This script take three parameter from user like command,username and Key

1) which command you want to run on multiple servers.

2) From which user you want to run this command.

3) It will ask for Key or Key path for ssh connection.

4) Host will check the hostname file and truncate the hostname where it finds(,) to the (\n)

5) It will make ssh connection and run command one by one on every single host.
